    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy when u put it that way. like, if we're just \"blips\" and it's all just an accident, then all the suffering we go through is just... unnecessary. why do we even have to endure the struggle of living if there's no purpose at the end of it? it feels like we're just being forced to participate in something that doesn't even care about us.",
